{"tid":2376931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【熱烈慶祝 武漢封城一週年】咁大件事無人講？","createTime":"2021-01-23T07:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T08:22:01.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8ee6547bfe5ecda9572068c2745c4a5eb5d9e6","tid":2376931,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>中共冷處理武漢封城一週年 上至習近平下至官媒幾乎噤聲</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img95.699pic.com/photo/40168/4367.gif_wh860.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg95.699pic.com%2Fphoto%2F40168%2F4367.gif_wh860.gif&h=5fa29127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/23 14:27<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">今天為武漢封城一週年，中國武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情還在燒，不過中共上至習近平，下至官媒，不是無人提起，就是全以正能量的方式來做報導，只剩中國網友的議論紛紛。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，在武漢封城一週年的這天，除了中共領導人習近平一字未提，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">中共較為主要的官媒，如新華社、人民日報、央視等，也保持靜默</span></span>，而習近平在十九屆中央紀委五次全會的談話，則不意外地被放在置頂的頭條區。<br />\n<br />\n中媒《新京報》是少數提起武漢封城一週年的媒體，並發表了標題為「武漢『封城』一周年：不負來之不易抗疫成果」的社論，不過內容不外乎是大讚當局防疫，直呼<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">「回顧這場驚心動魄的『戰疫』，以武漢『封城』為節點，全體國民與病毒展開了激烈的賽跑，並在強大信念支撐之下，取得了舉世矚目的成就」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖說中共官方並未提起，但有不少中國網友在微博貼文「1週年了」，並附上去年的媒體報導，對中共當局的抗疫成效有褒有貶，但鼓勵、肯定仍占大多數。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論家鍾原就在《新唐人》撰文，指出「重要的日子被中共政權刻意忽略，中共黨媒就當什麼事都沒發生過」，並認為中共高層反思的問題依然是政權生存與否，而非中國民眾和各國人民的生存。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3419897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3419897&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5JnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=f5cb214b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3419897&h=91159256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3419897</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">我們的偉大祖国 創造了世界最偉大成就！<br />\n要好好記著呢一日！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0610ed96d65b56093cf66a0b20ad016f57c994a","tid":2376931,"uid":139606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"有咩好post?"},{"pid":"93e3f8be3842639aaf7bca532e08fbe78d1aa12b","tid":2376931,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0610ed96d65b56093cf66a0b20ad016f57c994a","tid":2376931,"uid":139606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"有咩好post?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />維穩五毛現身了"},{"pid":"d54e7b14c7c6e5899f13f3ec4df851012f4217f2","tid":2376931,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"問我中蟈哪像染病"},{"pid":"01972e44a75f3b7fc76fdb01c361a83de09ed7ab","tid":2376931,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"漏夜搭頭班車大遷徙到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043b34cf5e08e546f5cfed1c034eb279128ed0c1","tid":2376931,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"無人講,咪唔好講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7412d6fac313b7eeac0b17f00b25ec980ca1a476","tid":2376931,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043b34cf5e08e546f5cfed1c034eb279128ed0c1","tid":2376931,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"無人講,咪唔好講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"SORRY,無睇內容,咁咪我講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2b874983e065fead75a34d7d2b51469ce90863","tid":2376931,"uid":273746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"